data.description: Massive single family on a corner lot with wrap-around font porch in an amazing walk-able location!  This well maintained property is filled with natural light and is currently being used as a two family that could be easily converted back to a single family.  Each floor is very spacious and features two bedrooms with additional potential.  Main floor features large entry, spacious living room, off-set bonus/game room and wrap around front porch.  Upper floor features large living room, two bedrooms, small balcony, and room to expand into the walk-up attic.  Also listed as a two family home MLS#1858576
